{"tid":32443,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人接受唔到女人口臭？","createTime":"2016-12-10T07:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T08:20:28.000Z","uid":947,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e1d9e2901e8b2d46836a143b599d2191d533feb","tid":32443,"uid":947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:39:41.000Z","msg":"一個男人，佢口臭，你會覺得好正常，可能佢唔係成日刷牙又或者冇飲水，係正常既男人味。<br />\n<br />\n但一個女人，佢口臭，你起馬都扣左佢10分（我會扣50分）<br />\n<br />\n點解？你試諗下佢一同你講野，佢個口入面既口臭味已經將你頭腦衝昏，無論佢幾靚，只要有口臭我敢講你一定對佢會反感（至少唔會有好感先）你係唔會再有任何意欲想同佢講野，因為你知道，你一再同佢講野又要瘋狂聞佢啲口臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n接受唔到女人口臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n接受到女人口臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864bdf4e68a2b3dbc69026ec2529badab1566273","tid":32443,"uid":947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:40:12.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打分享下聞過女人口臭既經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9a2e8eae521cc00d89630ba2b59ff61e0bc889","tid":32443,"uid":42085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:42:05.000Z","msg":"恕我見識少 未聽過男人口臭係男人味o既一種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係人口臭都應該扣分啦"},{"pid":"be69ca890282a9cfa86edc0843bbf120a7f889d6","tid":32443,"uid":48968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T08:07:21.000Z","msg":"中學嗰陣有個女同學佢有口臭，差唔多全班同學都會喺背後講佢，聽講仲有唔止一個人問過佢幾耐刷一次牙？今日有冇刷牙嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢嗰時有男朋友，有人仲問過佢男朋友點解會錫得落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實有口臭真喺幾難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777d4bd7fedf0f50e11f6e0ae2eb860713867efb","tid":32443,"uid":947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T08:11:57.000Z","msg":"